Sudoku Protocol Support (Xray inbound)
======================================

This directory vendors and adapts the official Sudoku protocol stack from:

  https://github.com/SUDOKU-ASCII/sudoku  (GPL-3.0-or-later)

and is intended to be wire-compatible with Mihomo's Sudoku client
(type: sudoku, Mihomo > v1.19.21).

IMPORTANT
---------
1. GPL-3.0 applies to the vendored protocol implementation under this tree.
   Distributing a binary that links this code may require releasing the
   combined work under GPL-3.0 terms. Review LICENSE obligations before
   shipping Fboard-Node / Xray-core builds that include this package.

2. This is NOT the Xray finalmask/sudoku appearance transform under
   transport/internet/finalmask/sudoku, which is a different, incompatible
   feature.

3. Do not imply official endorsement by the Sudoku project.
